  <brief_title>The Mechanism of TCF7L2 and SLC30A8 on Antipsychotic-induced Metabolic Syndrome</brief_title>
  <official_title>The Mechanism of TCF7L2 and SLC30A8 on Antipsychotic-induced Metabolic Syndrome</official_title>
  <sponsors>
